# Plagiarism Checker

## Overview

The Plagiarism Checker helps users identify duplicate or matching text by comparing submitted content against available sources. It is designed to support original writing and improve content quality before publishing or submission.

This tool is useful for students, teachers, bloggers, content creators, SEO professionals, and businesses.

## Features

* Detect duplicate content
* Highlight matching text
* Display originality percentage
* Easy-to-read plagiarism report
* Fast online scanning
* Mobile-friendly interface

## How to Use

1. Paste your text into the editor.
2. Click the **Check Plagiarism** button.
3. Wait for the scan to complete.
4. Review the plagiarism report and highlighted sections.
5. Edit your content to improve originality if necessary.

